{"tid":2200570,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人真係好鍾意食嘢","createTime":"2020-09-13T05:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T05:55:21.000Z","uid":365128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a77d4bbd8fe5bd41cf7fb6dc943f142a4bd0873f","tid":2200570,"uid":365128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:18:21.000Z","msg":"就係鍾意食嘢 間間餐廳都想試"},{"pid":"5fe560eddde8c7c4190e21b41da38fd9fb83e96c","tid":2200570,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:20:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">一齊google畀零分比香島中學 等啲家長揀嘅時候會考慮清楚</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n之前我地<span class=\"purple\"><strong>過百留言一一被delete</strong></span>，估計被google評為無效，請繼續追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">香島中學<br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/rpGUKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FrpGUKs&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513c2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=576f0a29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/rpGUKs</a><br />\n天水圍香島中學<br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/eNAKtm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FeNAKtm&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513c2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=0dd478ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/eNAKtm</a><br />\n將軍澳香島中學 <br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/C9Vm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FC9Vm&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513c2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=f261edca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/C9Vm</a></span>Z3<br />\n<br />\n留言:<br />\n事件一<br />\n校方帶頭將政治帶入校園，一名教師懷疑在音樂考試時未有禁止學生演奏「不恰當歌曲」而不獲續約。<br />\n<br />\n事件二<br />\n香島中學正校關注組指，9月7日一名中四學生突然被校長及訓導主任召回學校會面，校方指該名同學在網上溝通軟件Microsoft Team的簡介上填寫了抗爭口號，因而作出處分，包括立即停學一個星期，並向教育局通報。校方向該名學生表示，若然希望保留學位則需要記兩個大過，及警告再有發現參與社會運動，將會立即開除學籍。<br />\n<br />\n關注組成員又提到，校方曾多次警告該名學生不要參與社會活動，否則後果自負等；又指校方「敕令停課」的處分嚴重，形容是關注組成立後至今最嚴重的處分，指校方從未有處分關注組的成員或對抗校方的同學，故對校方處分「平平無奇」的學生感到詫異。"},{"pid":"a52d612a5f7625a5abfe135a18d14e8af59e8b6a","tid":2200570,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:55:21.000Z","msg":"返工要成日去唔同區食嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}